@startuml
title Sequence systeme - Consultation notifications

actor Patient
boundary "Frontend React" as FE
control "Backend API" as API
database "Base de donnees" as DB
control "Service IA prive" as AI

Patient -> FE : Ouvrir /notifications
FE -> API : GET /notifications
API -> DB : Charger alertes patient
DB --> API : Liste notifications
API --> FE : Notifications
FE --> Patient : Afficher centre d'alertes

Patient -> FE : Filtrer "Critiques" / "Non lues"
FE -> FE : Filtrer localement
FE --> Patient : Afficher resultat

Patient -> FE : Marquer comme lu
FE -> API : PATCH /notifications/:id/read
API -> DB : Mettre read=true
DB --> API : OK
API --> FE : Notification mise a jour
FE --> Patient : Feedback succes

AI --> DB : Creer alertes IA si anomalie detectee

@enduml
